{{Infobox organization |name = Bangladesh Copyright Office |image = |image_border = |size = |alt = |caption = |map = |msize = |malt = |mcaption = |abbreviation = |motto = |formation = 1971 |extinction = |type = |status = |purpose = |headquarters = [[Dhaka]], [[Bangladesh]] |location = |coords = <!-- Coordinates of location using a coordinates template --> |region_served = Bangladesh |members = |language = Bengali |leader_title = |leader_name = |main_organ = |parent_organization = |affiliations = |num_staff = |num_volunteers = |budget = |website = [http://www.copyrightoffice.gov.bd/ Bangladesh Copyright Office] |remarks = }}
'''Bangladesh Copyright Office''' national level [[quasi-judicial]] organisation responsible for copyright management in Bangladesh and is located in [[Dhaka]], [[Bangladesh]].<ref name="qws">{{cite web|title=Copyright|url=http://en.banglapedia.org/index.php?title=Copyright|website=en.banglapedia.org|publisher=Banglapedia|accessdate=27 October 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Microsoft signs agreement with BCS to promote “Genuine Software”|url=http://www.thedailystar.net/bytes/tech-happening/microsoft-signs-agreement-bcs-promote-%E2%80%9Cgenuine-software%E2%80%9D-75224|website=thedailystar.net|publisher=The Daily Star|accessdate=27 October 2016|date=2 April 2015}}</ref>
==History== After the independence of Bangladesh in 1971 the regional copyright office was made the national copyright office. It is a department under the ministry of culture.<ref name="qws"></ref> It has been criticized for failing to coordinate with the [[Department of Patents, Designs and Trademarks]], both of which are responsible for the protection of intellectual property in Bangladesh.<ref>{{cite web|last1=Towhidul Islam|first1=Mohammad|title=TRIPS Agreement and Bangladesh|url=http://www.thedailystar.net/law-our-rights/trips-agreement-and-bangladesh-210949|website=thedailystar.net|publisher=The Daily Star|accessdate=27 October 2016|date=2 February 2016}}</ref> Copyright applications are available on its website.<ref>{{cite web|title=Legal protection of databases|url=http://www.thedailystar.net/law-our-rights/legal-protection-databases-1235332|website=thedailystar.net|publisher=The Daily Star|accessdate=27 October 2016|date=7 June 2016}}</ref>
